      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Vladimir Medvedev</b>\n</p><p><b>Vladimir R. Medvedev</b>,<br />\na Russian games and chess programmer, and author of the chess program <a href=\"/GreKo\" title=\"GreKo\">GreKo</a>, first released on April 01, 2002 <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>. However, Vladimir already started some chess programming in 2000 <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>, with the aim to write a standalone chess program with an own <a href=\"/GUI\" title=\"GUI\">GUI</a> using <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Microsoft_Foundation_Class_Library\">MFC</a>, but implemented an <a href=\"/Othello\" title=\"Othello\">Othello</a>  applet in <a href=\"/Java\" title=\"Java\">Java</a> first <sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>. On one of his download sites, Vladimir does not only provide GreKo, but also a <a href=\"/Kaissa\" title=\"Kaissa\">Kaissa</a> <a href=\"/IBM_PC\" title=\"IBM PC\">PC</a> port in <a href=\"/C\" title=\"C\">Turbo C</a> from 1992, and a listing of the <a href=\"/ITEP_Chess_Program\" title=\"ITEP Chess Program\">ITEP Chess Program</a> for the <a href=\"/M-20\" title=\"M-20\">M-20</a> computer <sup id=\"cite_ref-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup> <sup id=\"cite_ref-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup>.\nVladimir further published <a href=\"/Learning\" title=\"Learning\">machine learning</a> related articles on determining <a href=\"/Point_Value\" title=\"Point Value\">point values</a> by <a href=\"/Automated_Tuning#LogisticRegression\" title=\"Automated Tuning\">logistic regression</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-6\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup> and <a href=\"/Texel%27s_Tuning_Method\" title=\"Texel&#39;s Tuning Method\">Texel's Tuning Method</a> as applied to <a href=\"/GreKo\" title=\"GreKo\">GreKo</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-7\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-7\">&#91;7&#93;</a></sup> in the popular Russian IT portal <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Habrahabr\">Habrahabr</a>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#See_also\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">See also</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Forum_Posts\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Forum Posts</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#2000_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2000 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#2010_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2010 ...</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"See_also\">See also</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Vladimir_Medvedev&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: See also\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/GreKo\" title=\"GreKo\">GreKo</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Point_Value_by_Regression_Analysis\" title=\"Point Value by Regression Analysis\">Point Value by Regression Analysis</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Vladimir_Medvedev&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2000_...\">2000 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Vladimir_Medvedev&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: 2000 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://groups.google.com/d/msg/rec.games.chess.computer/5w73imoX8iU/oZhBonZLQUIJ\">hashing function</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Vladimir R. Medvedev</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">rgcc</a>, October 17, 2000&#160;» <a href=\"/Transposition_Table\" title=\"Transposition Table\">Transposition Table</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://groups.google.com/d/msg/rec.games.chess.computer/yHBbFa1GcSo/nkiYjGAo30sJ\">GreKo chess engine</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Vladimir R. Medvedev</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">rgcc</a>, April 01, 2002 </li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=239987\">Repetitions: is this code correct?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Vladimir Medvedev</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, July 12, 2002&#160;» <a href=\"/Repetitions\" title=\"Repetitions\">Repetitions</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=266544\">Ultra small pawn hash efficiency</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Vladimir Medvedev</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, November 21, 2002&#160;» <a href=\"/Pawn_Hash_Table\" title=\"Pawn Hash Table\">Pawn Hash Table</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-aurec.com/wbforum/viewtopic.php?f=4&amp;t=3795\">What is \"history pruning\"?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Vladimir Medvedev</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">Winboard Forum</a>, November 07, 2005&#160;» <a href=\"/Late_Move_Reductions\" title=\"Late Move Reductions\">Late Move Reductions</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2010_...\">2010 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Vladimir_Medvedev&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: 2010 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=54386\">Data structures for parallel search?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Vladimir Medvedev</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, November 19, 2014</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-aurec.com/wbforum/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=53335\">New site for GreKo</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Vladimir Medvedev</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">Winboard Forum</a>, January 14, 2015</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=56168\">Piece weights with regression analysis (in Russian)</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Vladimir Medvedev</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, April 30, 2015&#160;» <a href=\"/Point_Value_by_Regression_Analysis\" title=\"Point Value by Regression Analysis\">Point Value by Regression Analysis</a> </li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=60902\">GreKo 2015 ML: tuning evaluation (article in Russian)</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Vladimir Medvedev</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, July 22, 2016&#160;» <a href=\"/Texel%27s_Tuning_Method\" title=\"Texel&#39;s Tuning Method\">Texel's Tuning Method</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=68277\">GreKo 2018.08</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Vladimir Medvedev</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 22, 2018</li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Vladimir_Medvedev&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://greko.su/\">GreKo chess engine</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-8\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-8\">&#91;8&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://greko.sourceforge.net/\">SourceForge.net: GreKo - Project Web Hosting - Open Source Software</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.sdchess.ru/Greko.htm\">Greko by Vladimir Medvedev, Russia</a> from <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.sdchess.ru/\">sdchess.ru</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://habrahabr.ru/post/254753/\">Определяем веса шахматных фигур регрессионным анализом / Хабрахабр</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Vladimir Medvedev</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Habrahabr\">Habrahabr</a>, April 27, 2015 (Russian)&#160;» <a href=\"/Point_Value_by_Regression_Analysis\" title=\"Point Value by Regression Analysis\">Point Value by Regression Analysis</a></li></ul>\n<dl><dd> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://github.com/WinPooh/pgnlearn\">WinPooh/pgnlearn · GitHub</a></dd></dl>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://habrahabr.ru/post/305604/\">Самообучение шахматной программы / Хабрахабр</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Vladimir Medvedev</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Habrahabr\">Habrahabr</a>, July 21, 2016 (Russian)&#160;» <a href=\"/Texel%27s_Tuning_Method\" title=\"Texel&#39;s Tuning Method\">Texel's Tuning Method</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Vladimir_Medvedev&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://groups.google.com/d/msg/rec.games.chess.computer/yHBbFa1GcSo/nkiYjGAo30sJ\">GreKo chess engine</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Vladimir R. Medvedev</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">rgcc</a>, April 01, 2002 </span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://groups.google.com/d/msg/rec.games.chess.computer/5w73imoX8iU/oZhBonZLQUIJ\">hashing function</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Vladimir R. Medvedev</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">rgcc</a>, October 17, 2000</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=51837&amp;start=5\">Re: GreKo 12.0 2002-2014 12 years development, Congrats!</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Vladimir Medvedev</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, April 03, 2014</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-4\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://sites.google.com/site/grekochess/\">GreKo - Download</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-5\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.computer-museum.ru/english/m20.htm\">M-20 Computer</a> from <a href=\"/Russian_Virtual_Computer_Museum\" title=\"Russian Virtual Computer Museum\">Russian Virtual Computer Museum</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-6\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-6\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://habrahabr.ru/post/254753/\">Определяем веса шахматных фигур регрессионным анализом / Хабрахабр</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Vladimir Medvedev</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Habrahabr\">Habrahabr</a>, April 27, 2015( Russian)&#160;» <a href=\"/Point_Value_by_Regression_Analysis\" title=\"Point Value by Regression Analysis\">Point Value by Regression Analysis</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-7\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-7\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://habrahabr.ru/post/305604/\">Самообучение шахматной программы / Хабрахабр</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Vladimir Medvedev</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Habrahabr\">Habrahabr</a>, July 21, 2016 (Russian)&#160;» <a href=\"/Texel%27s_Tuning_Method\" title=\